from Jens Gelhaar:

One Ioda was designed by Sue/Susan LaPorte at CalArts in 1991/2 or so. The best way to find her – apart from googling – would be to contact the Alumni department at CalArts, at [alumni@calarts.edu](mailto:alumni@calarts.edu).

LaPorte is now at the College for Creative Studies. [CCS](http://web.archive.org/web/20070804143119/http:/www.ccscad.edu/)
